title.rendered: DRIVETECH 4X4 HIGH LIFT JACK SPARE WHEEL MOUNT

content.rendered:
DRIVETECH 4X4 HIGH LIFT JACK SPARE WHEEL MOUNT

Drivetech 4×4 High Lift Jack Spare Wheel Mount available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

For use with Drivetech 4×4 high lift jack. Provides a solid mounting place using the rear wheel carrier found on most 4wd models. Does not require removal of the spare wheel to install.

CLICK HERE to view the full range of products available for your 4×4!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
